sessions.description: Master Yoda introduces you to the initial steps as a Jedi, including balancing on one hand, elevating objects, and deciphering his speech.
sessions.title: Focus, You Must

sessions.description: Princess Leia will discuss the burdens and joys of authority and royal grace in a time of galactic turmoil and intrigue. She asks that no one use the phrase 'Well, EXCUSE me Princess'.
sessions.title: Appreciation of Power

sessions.description:
Attendees are encouraged to also attend Pricess Leia's discussion 'Gender Roles in a Galactic Setting'. 
 Master Windu discusses controversial racial topics including the average ear length of the Gungan, the avian or amphibian heritage of the Ishi Tib, and mysterious lack of information on the 'Yoda Species.'
sessions.title: Race Issues in a Galactic Setting

sessions.description: Mr. Chewbaca's discussion will be interactive and participatory. He will discuss combat techniques and threat identification. Emergency medical personnel will be present during this... presentation.
sessions.title: Ahhh EaaaaY EERrrrraaaahhhh!!

sessions.description: Princess Leia summarizes the complexities of evolving gender issues for the Galactic Federation species. She delves into the unique challenges faced by races with 3+ genders and the cultural differences for mono-gender races. Attendees are encouraged to also attend Master Windu's discussion 'Race Issues in a Galactic Setting'.
sessions.title: Gender Roles in a Galactic Setting

sessions.description: Captain Solo discusses his experience with aging and flight and provides advice on how to do both with grace
sessions.title: Aging Gracefully as a Pilot

sessions.description: Master Windu will illustrate how to balance power with confidence as he repeats his amazing lines like 'This Party's Over' and 'You are under arrest, my lord.'
sessions.title: Balancing Power with Confidence

sessions.description: Master Yoda provides an interactive discussion on reclusivity, meditation, and patience. This 5 hour session will begin a 2 minute introduction and about 5 hours of silently stacking round stones.... by yourself.
sessions.title: In Appreciation of Reclusivity

sessions.description: Our highly successful and renown speakers take time to discuss lighter topics. They open up to our attendees by discussing their social delights, indulgences, and eccentricities in a galaxy of almost infinite pleasures.
sessions.title: Social Networking, Light Sabers, Podracing - How to Find Joy in the Galaxy

sessions.description: Mr. Solo discusses what is needed to manage your own trade route: charm, phase blasters, a large and hairy co-pilot, and old ship, and disreputable 'partners'.
sessions.title: Managing Trade and Relationships

sessions.description: Mr. Chewbaca's talk will be extemporaneous. Guests are encouraged to bring notepads and phase blasters.
sessions.title: EEhhhhaaeeerrrrrrr Ah

sessions.description: Our speakers willingly debate galactically contentious issues around technology including Clone armies, regulations around Death Star proliferation, and cyborg-cyborg marriage petitions.
sessions.title: The Moral Imperative of Advancing Technology

speakers.bio: Mr. Chewbaca is a powerful ally to Captain Solo and is often referred to as the more charming of the two.
speakers.name: Chewie Chewbaca
speakers.title: Engineer First Class, Ship's Mate of the Millennium Falcon

speakers.bio: Captain Solo is an accomplished pilot and vital ally to the Jedi. His exploits are galaxy renown and his flight skills unparalleled.
speakers.name: Han Solo
speakers.title: Trading Merchant, Alleged Smuggler, Captain of the Millennium Falcon

speakers.bio: Princess Leia is a galactic figure with her powerful ancestry, royal authority, latent Jedi abilities, and nerd-catching good-looks.
speakers.name: Leia Organa
speakers.title: Princess of Alderaan, Imperial Senator, General of Rebel Resistance, Chief of State of the New Republic

speakers.bio: Mace Windu, 2nd to only Master Yoda on the Jedi Council, is an accomplished commander, Jedi, and smooth operator.
speakers.name: Master Mace Windu
speakers.title: Jedi Master, Senior Jedi Councilor, Galactic Peace Officer

speakers.bio: Master Yoda is a small, green Jedi Master. You know him, you love him, and you barely understand him.
speakers.name: Master Yoda
speakers.title: Jedi Master, Lead Jedi Councilor, Galactic Peace Officer
